{"tid":1268772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回血] 想以死相諫嘅你 請入一入黎先","createTime":"2019-06-30T11:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T22:43:10.000Z","uid":36118,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"beb01483d91e3d42673f6fa8233d188daec35840","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"首先 我想同你講一句 <br />\n多謝你一直以黎嘅付出<br />\n你已經做得好好<br />\n<br />\n一切都唔係你嘅錯 <br />\n而係港共廢青廢中廢老嘅錯<br />\n係佢地無知嘅錯<br />\n係佢地對香港局勢視若無睹嘅錯<br />\n所以 唔好走到死呢一步<br />\n因為你值得繼續生活落去<br />\n要學識休息 真係要俾自己抖下<br />\n我地好需要你<br />\n<br />\n加上 死對呢件事根本冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 回帶返六四 中共派軍隊殺死天安門嘅學生市民<br />\n三十年過去 當初話要爭取嘅民主呢 乜都冇<br />\n佢地當冇事發生過 繼續封鎖消息<br />\n今次反送中 港共間接推我地去死 間接令烈士犧牲<br />\n雖然生命好寶貴<br />\n但試問一下咁冷血嘅國家 <br />\n又點會在乎我地條生命？<br />\n佢地只會無視你嘅犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但請緊記 我地每一位手足都好重視你<br />\n所以唔好犧牲呀<br />\n<br />\n第二 犧牲只會有反效果<br />\n知道你地有部分人想用死 引起更多港豬注意<br />\n坦白講 已經有兩個烈士犧牲左<br />\n班港豬要醒嘅亦都應該一早醒左<br />\n但現實係殘酷嘅<br />\n佢地只會care邊個泡菜明星發生咩事<br />\n深圳邊到好玩好食<br />\n而且呢家連登充斥住大量負面post<br />\n香港人都越黎越氣餒<br />\n烈士嘅死只會令在乎嘅人感到抑鬱<br />\n負擔情緒再蔓延 就會更多手足想尋死<br />\n當犧牲數字上升 人類只會更麻木<br />\n就好似學生自殺一樣 大家已經習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地就越黎越少人<br />\n<br />\n如果真係頂唔順嘅你 放自己一個假啦<br />\nDel埋連登 唔好睇social media<br />\n做你平時鍾意做嘅野<br />\n打波 踢波 睇Netflix 睇電影 打機 聽歌 唱K 旅行 行山<br />\nShopping 扮靚  <br />\n俾自己抖下 發洩下<br />\n冇野俾你地條命更加重要<br />\n記住 我地絕對唔會怪你<br />\n所以你都唔洗感到內疚<br />\n少一個 就真係少左一個㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n你已經做得好好了 <br />\n我地一個都不能少<br />\n你先休息<br />\n我地會一直做你嘅後盾<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有心事嘅放低哂係到 我地一齊分擔<br />\n絕對唔會俾任何一位手足獨自承受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 多謝咁多位真&middot;香港人一直以來嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0yGrr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0yGrr.png&h=e606b01b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa2ef7f20de963798c9f457124bf306ed0ece99d","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58617b96ce67a160dee7459c91ab51c893355175","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad828ae666b6296841f178db727d4d2b6a64d2c9","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480df8c3cae6f573983da18cab09ce09baef2433","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc5aa8d40889bb10bec906f519c2a85616b9c5e","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6a3d02ae958628d62b9e77bef973103173b4d8","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bfb4388b65d66e18af02a58c0aa44b6910336f","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"唔好再咁傻了 我地愛你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0c1f81a4b12f702b0ffb702cf688b2334ce1d8","tid":1268772,"uid":36118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-3